    {
      "type": "note",
      "id": "USjVJ",
      "x": 13280,
      "y": 0,
      "name": "note_update_prompt",
      "width": 300,
      "height": 190,
      "content": "In-app update prompt — SHIPPED form (PR #276), current-Arc pattern:\n\nLEFT column = resting state: a slim 24px centered pill above the sidebar Settings row, visible only while an update is READY (downloaded). Quiet: 60% sidebar-selected fill, 11px fg-2 label.\n\nRIGHT column = hover/keyboard-focus state: the pill morphs into the full card — bottom-anchored over the pill, growing upward, so pill and card are never visible at once. Click pins it open (focus-within). × dismisses per launch; pill returns next launch until installed.\n\nCard: header band (centered 11px title + ×), divider, centered neutral checkbox (NO accent), slim full-width accent glow 'Restart and Update' button. Checkbox mirrors About's auto-install toggle — one storage key, two surfaces."
    },
